Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.87,0:02:19.86,STAFF,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间: 白色猎人  若草
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.87,0:02:19.86,STAFF,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翻译: 凉菜  Leader  校对: Potianwu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.03,0:02:45.00,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#4  合宿！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.26,0:24:19.61,next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)}#5         顾问！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.09,0:00:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.71,0:00:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到海边了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.74,0:00:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.00,0:00:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪闪发光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.25,0:00:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  游泳咯~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.50,0:00:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.76,0:00:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.87,0:00:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别闹得太过分了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.00,0:00:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯  水是咸的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.25,0:00:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海水  这就是海水啊  小律
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.43,0:00:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是海浪哦海浪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.48,0:00:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是海浪啊小律
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.43,0:00:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当…当我的话是耳旁风啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.87,0:02:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？  轻音部…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.01,0:02:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱高祭？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.00,0:02:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.64,0:02:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指头…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.20,0:02:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的忘了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.43,0:03:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我小时候经常被奶奶夸来着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.08,0:03:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说「小唯啊  记一件事忘十件事」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.06,0:03:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…不是在夸奖吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.13,0:03:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小澪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.89,0:03:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪儿了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.87,0:03:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要组织一次合宿！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.98,0:03:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合宿？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.89,0:03:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  马上就是暑假了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.45,0:03:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非要去海边？还是要去爬山？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.25,0:03:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是去玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.56,0:03:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是乐队的强化训练合宿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.30,0:03:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我从早到晚老老实实地练习
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.22,0:03:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  得去买新衣服了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.07,0:03:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泳装也要买新的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.00,0:03:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们倒是听我说啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.24,0:03:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假结束之后紧跟着不就是学园祭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.81,0:03:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学园祭…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.53,0:03:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  要说起樱高祭的轻音部演奏会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.42,0:03:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前可是很有名的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.13,0:03:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如…此…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.53,0:03:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学园祭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.67,0:03:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中的学园祭很好玩的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.79,0:03:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,模拟商店
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.01,0:03:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炒面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.70,0:04:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,章鱼烧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.12,0:04:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我提议我提议  搞女仆咖啡店！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.17,0:04:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想办鬼屋啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.40,0:04:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女仆咖啡店！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.46,0:04:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼屋！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.87,0:04:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女仆咖啡店！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.18,0:04:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼屋！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.63,0:04:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女仆咖啡店肯定要更加…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.37,0:04:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为啥只有人家挨打？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.32,0:04:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是轻音部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.50,0:04:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要搞的是演奏会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.63,0:04:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  我迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.67,0:04:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…要不要吃松糕？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.16,0:04:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.17,0:04:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紬  你是怎么想的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.19,0:04:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说要循序渐进  可这已经三个多月了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.89,0:04:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都还没有练习过一次合奏  这也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.29,0:04:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了算了算了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.96,0:04:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六遍…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.03,0:04:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…那就去吧  好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.98,0:04:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和大家一起过夜一直都是我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.77,0:04:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.67,0:05:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样就去海边吧  或者去…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.11,0:05:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了这是乐队的强化合宿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.68,0:05:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过大概要花多少钱啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.52,0:05:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊  会不会有困难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.46,0:05:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.49,0:05:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小紬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.92,0:05:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.98,0:05:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别墅啥的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.98,0:05:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.69,0:05:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.56,0:05:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.41,0:05:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是该起床了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.17,0:05:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来你穿的不是我的睡衣么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.04,0:05:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再睡一会儿…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.18,0:05:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.40,0:05:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.53,0:05:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在几点？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.02,0:05:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.16,0:06:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.21,0:06:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您「早」…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.62,0:06:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.64,0:06:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啦~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.16,0:06:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  总算是赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.36,0:06:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千叮咛万嘱咐叫你不要迟到的说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.45,0:06:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  晚上兴奋得睡不着啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.92,0:06:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  又不是小学生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.35,0:06:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…好像还有一个小学生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.70,0:06:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小紬…都说了这是她的梦想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.72,0:06:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凝胶状的真好~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.43,0:06:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凝胶？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.74,0:06:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做什么样的梦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.39,0:06:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  拍张照片留下这一刻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.24,0:06:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样啦  太可怜啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.73,0:06:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留个纪念留个纪念
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.30,0:07:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.41,0:07:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看把她弄醒了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.48,0:07:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.25,0:07:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  是不是该告诉我们啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.73,0:07:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个别墅在哪里啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.92,0:07:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.90,0:07:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.63,0:07:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.56,0:07:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大海啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.15,0:07:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是大海
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.82,0:07:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.23,0:07:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  一~二
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.95,0:07:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  是海的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.75,0:07:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要游个痛快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.45,0:07:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了不是来玩的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.01,0:08:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真够大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.70,0:08:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实本来想安排更大的地方来着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.91,0:08:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后只借到了最小的一幢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.75,0:08:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是…最「小」的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.71,0:08:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真宽敞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.39,0:08:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太强了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.52,0:08:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.67,0:08:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.77,0:08:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都说了不用准备什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.32,0:08:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.82,0:08:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主床耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.85,0:08:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.28,0:08:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着就要流口水
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.04,0:08:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.45,0:08:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直嘱咐尽量不要准备得太夸张
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.33,0:09:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们总是不太明白我的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.32,0:09:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.96,0:09:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一段时间没用过了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.55,0:09:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以有点担心还能不能用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.38,0:09:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  看起来没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  唯和律上哪儿去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才就不见了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.69,0:09:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿她们没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.65,0:09:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.15,0:09:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.02,0:09:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的轻音部在学园祭时候的演出
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.47,0:09:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前在社团活动室发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.18,0:09:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.79,0:09:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起我们要好很多…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.37,0:09:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得听了之后　有一种不想输给他们的想法…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.92,0:09:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才提出要组织合宿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.37,0:10:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.97,0:10:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想我们不会输给他们的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.04,0:10:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.24,0:10:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紬…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.60,0:10:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  开玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.84,0:10:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.26,0:10:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真快…练习怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.43,0:10:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们先走一步
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.77,0:10:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两位也快点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.79,0:10:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就凭这两位同志？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.17,0:10:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.93,0:10:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.59,0:10:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.87,0:10:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.93,0:10:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪  一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.45,0:10:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？  紬你真的打算去？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.85,0:10:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得来一次  稍微玩一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.73,0:10:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.93,0:10:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.79,0:10:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紬  快来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.45,0:10:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们等你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.41,0:11:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家也要去～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.26,0:11:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到达无人岛后已经过了两周
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.14,0:11:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被冲走的时候还以为死定了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.46,0:11:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是总觉得这样也挺有趣的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.38,0:11:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  发现个大家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.14,0:11:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.49,0:11:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢天谢地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.54,0:11:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在乱设定个什么劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.73,0:11:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.77,0:11:47.14,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波霸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.18,0:11:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.88,0:11:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯  我们去游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.29,0:11:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.85,0:11:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.94,0:11:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.05,0:12:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个美丽的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.98,0:12:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  你画了什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.24,0:12:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不觉就变成这样了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.10,0:12:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不怕不怕不怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.43,0:12:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到医生那一检查  膝盖打开后密密麻麻爬满了藤壶…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.43,0:12:34.12,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤壶是附着在海边岩石上的一簇簇灰白色的有石灰质外壳的小动物\N就是刚才小澪摸到的那些
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.81,0:12:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  游爽了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.98,0:12:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于到了  黄金之岛吉潘古
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.98,0:12:49.39,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄金之岛吉潘古：即日本  马可波罗的《东方见闻录》曾将日本认为是\N离中国东方1500海里处的黄金之岛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.47,0:12:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差得远呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.47,0:12:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  啥时候搬来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.12,0:12:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得来到海边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.08,0:12:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不玩个痛快  来的意义就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.97,0:13:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  练习！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.92,0:13:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.23,0:13:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「真是的  都是因为律那么爱玩」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.35,0:13:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩得最尽兴的是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.92,0:13:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.58,0:13:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  吃得好饱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.30,0:13:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  地上凉凉的好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.20,0:13:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样闭上眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.33,0:13:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉会被海浪带走呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.47,0:13:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  真的耶  晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.33,0:13:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.89,0:13:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要开始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.52,0:13:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两位都起来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.85,0:13:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紬  稍微让一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.74,0:13:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  今天还是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.38,0:14:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了练习才到这里来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.43,0:14:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.42,0:14:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  律啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近是不是胖了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.47,0:14:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是肚子那一块啥的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.52,0:14:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是因为最近没有打鼓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.81,0:14:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经拿不动吉他了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.51,0:14:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这把吉他很重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.21,0:14:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就叫你买个轻的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.91,0:14:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁说要买这吉他的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.08,0:14:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.01,0:14:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地板该变热了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.86,0:14:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转啊转  团团转
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.60,0:14:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要弄脏的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈  又变凉快了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.85,0:14:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去  学园祭要怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.13,0:14:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了就女仆咖啡店好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.42,0:14:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是鬼屋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.94,0:14:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯  你可是有所不知
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.40,0:15:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看澪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.78,0:15:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是突然搞什么啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.16,0:15:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像澪这么适合女仆装的人可是稀有物种啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.65,0:15:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑长筒袜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.29,0:15:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯白的围裙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.88,0:15:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有女仆发圈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.82,0:15:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萌萌～啾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.90,0:15:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再配上这么个台词
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.94,0:15:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.20,0:15:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.87,0:15:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律队员…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.53,0:15:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这之后真的要练习了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.29,0:15:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.50,0:15:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一  二
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.29,0:15:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就由我奉上最后一曲  来咯~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.47,0:16:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢耶噢耶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.78,0:16:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  已经结束了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.34,0:16:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱就这么点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.37,0:16:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后还有机会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.36,0:16:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得对  在武道馆公演时要华丽地啪啪啪啪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.32,0:16:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武道馆？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.78,0:16:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  不是说好了那里就是目标吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.43,0:16:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.81,0:16:58.90,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1500,1000)}「目标  武道馆!!」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.89,0:17:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 到了时候我要穿粉红色的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.40,0:17:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是小学生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.74,0:17:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不觉得很可爱嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.69,0:17:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太孩子气了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.52,0:17:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也觉得粉红的有一点…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.66,0:17:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.46,0:17:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标是武道馆的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.44,0:17:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先必须要练到这个程度
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.82,0:17:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  弹得真好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.83,0:17:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  但是这曲子…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.94,0:17:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小的们久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.33,0:17:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.23,0:17:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,磁带转到B面了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.92,0:17:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.06,0:17:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听不到听不到…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.26,0:17:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤壶  在膝盖的里面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.61,0:17:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊…不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.77,0:18:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.00,0:18:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩过火了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.03,0:18:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.46,0:18:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啊  澪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.61,0:18:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪  没有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.96,0:18:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是妖怪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.93,0:18:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.35,0:18:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直中靶心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.35,0:18:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萌萌～啾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.44,0:18:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  澪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.91,0:18:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯  刚才的曲子真的能…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.37,0:18:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  看着哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.58,0:18:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗…人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.65,0:19:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.76,0:19:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害  完美
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.48,0:19:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  「喵」的地方不太明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.60,0:19:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「喵」？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.38,0:19:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那应该是用了推弦的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.85,0:19:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锁喉？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.85,0:19:16.12,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日文中「锁喉」和「推弦」两者同音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.22,0:19:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.25,0:19:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓推弦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.26,0:19:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在弦发出声音后再推动弦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.80,0:19:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一推…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.07,0:19:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.18,0:19:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.30,0:19:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.44,0:19:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.38,0:19:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.99,0:19:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.50,0:19:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像正中笑穴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.11,0:19:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤壶？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.11,0:19:49.12,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑穴和壶同音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.47,0:19:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到连露天浴场都有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.26,0:20:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天过得真愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.99,0:20:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  就像紬说的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.52,0:20:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能不需要那么担心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.41,0:20:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我说就应该再多玩一会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.61,0:20:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.88,0:20:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.08,0:20:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刘海太长了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.57,0:20:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.30,0:20:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这样也出乎意料的可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.61,0:20:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  还有出乎意料是什么意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.97,0:20:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对不起 不觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.96,0:20:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.33,0:20:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.25,0:20:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就明白啊  好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.43,0:20:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后就是无名指啪地一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.37,0:20:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.00,0:20:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.86,0:20:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音乐果然棒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.56,0:20:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天第一次和大家一起练习
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.62,0:20:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.06,0:20:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.41,0:21:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏小澪提出合宿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.47,0:21:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.90,0:21:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.87,0:21:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪在害羞哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.02,0:21:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢  热气上头了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.51,0:21:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.06,0:21:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了不是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.52,0:21:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪怒了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.48,0:21:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.72,0:21:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.94,0:21:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  好可怕～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.72,0:21:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.39,0:21:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.56,0:21:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了  稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.45,0:21:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说合宿的照片冲好了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.99,0:21:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  给
